<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HMUN SANG CHIN AH CH268</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Cunglei ram cu ka panh lengmang, Nifa te-in hmun sang ka phan, Thlacam
 pah in ka fuh hnu ah, Bawipa hmunsang ah ka dirter.

[C1]
   Bawipa, ka thawh law dir tuah ning, Zumhnak in vancung ram nuam ah,
   Ka phanh bal lo mi ram ah cun, Bawipa, hmunsang chin ka phanhter.

[V2]
 Tihphannak ram mui chungah hin, Sau deuh um cu ka zuam ti lo, Mi cheu
 nih um duh hmanh hna seh, Kei tinhmi cu hmunsang a si.

[C2]
   Bawipa, ka thawh law dir tuah ning, Zumhnak in vancung ram nuam ah,
   Ka phanh bal lo mi ram ah cun, Bawipa, hmunsang chin ka phanhter.

[V3]
 Satan sual thurnak tong hmanhning, Va bang a sang in zuan ka duh,
 Mithiang mi hla sak thawng hna cu, Zumhnak hnathlam in ka theih cang.

[C3]
   Bawipa, ka thawh law dir tuah ning, Zumhnak in vancung ram nuam ah,
   Ka phanh bal lo mi ram ah cun, Bawipa, hmunsang chin ka phanhter.

[V4]
 A sannak bik ram cu phan in, Sunpar ceunak cu co ka duh, Vanram phanh
 tiang thlacam pah in, Bawipa hmunsang ah ka hruai ko.

[C4]
   Bawipa, ka thawh law dir tuah ning, Zumhnak in vancung ram nuam ah,
   Ka phanh bal lo mi ram ah cun, Bawipa, hmunsang chin ka phanhter.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
<hymn_number>268</hymn_number>
</song>